text: Zeferino Antunes Flores is a Mexican politician from the Party of the Democratic Revolution. From 2002 to 2003 he served as Deputy of the LVIII Legislature of the Mexican Congress representing the State of Mexico. ==References== Category:Date of birth unknown Category:Living people Category:Politicians from the State of Mexico Category:Members of the Chamber of Deputies (Mexico) Category:Party of the Democratic Revolution politicians Category:21st-century Mexican politicians Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
